---
title: All-American Crumbed Chicken Burger with Fries & Garlic Aioli
description: You've been dreaming of a All-American flavoured crumbed chicken burger? Well how about that – so have we! And we promise
you, with a crispy panko coating, creamy aioli and oven-baked fries, it tastes even better in real life than we had imagined.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/all-american-crumbed-chicken-burger-122a5e51.jpg
